The paper focuses on optimizing queries over video for spatiotemporal information of objects using deep learning techniques. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses query optimization techniques and the use of specialized neural networks, which are relevant to the database (cs.DB), multimedia (cs.MM), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
